Once again I am going friends only. After recent issues with non LJ friends and the fact that I write down where I work. I have decided that it is the best thing. Plus, I would like to know who is reading. 

For those of you who aren't friends just comment and I will add you. I rarely ever say no, so don't feel intimidated. 

On top of going FO on all of you I am also cleaning out my friends list. Feel free to comment if you want to stay.
